<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>EMA624_06_IH_0004</title>

		<!-- 공통 js-->
		<script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
		<script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

		<!-- 공통 css-->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

		<!-- 개별 -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema624_06.css" />
	</head>

	<body>
		<div id="app_wrap" class="ema624_06_ih_0004">
			<section class="title type2">
				<h2 data-head="4_deep_green" lang="y">
					음료수 6개를 3600원에 팔고 있습니다. 이 음료수 10개의 가격은 얼마인지 비례식을 세우고 답을 구해
					보세요.
				</h2>
			</section>

			<section class="contents">
				<div class="question_box justify_center">
					<div class="flex align_start gap_10">
						<span lang="y" class="label_gray">비례식</span>
						<div class="input_wrap input1">
							<math-field></math-field>
							<div class="example_box">
								<p>6:3600=10:□</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="flex align_start gap_10">
						<span lang="y" class="label_gray">답</span>
						<div class="input_wrap input2">
							<math-field></math-field>
							<div class="example_box">
								<p>6000</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<!-- 해설 -->
				<div class="solve_area">
					<div class="inner_solve">
						<div class="flex">
							<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
							<div class="conts_solve">
								<p>음료수 10개의 가격을 <span class="nemo"></span>원이라 하고 비례식을 세우면
								   6 : 3600 = 10 : <span class="nemo"></span>입니다.</p>
								<p>6 × <span class="nemo"></span> = 3600 × 10, 6 × <span class="nemo"></span> = 36000,
									<span class="nemo"></span> = 6000이므로 음료수 10개의 가격은 6000원입니다.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="btn_area">
					<button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
					<button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
					<button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
